# Instagram Messages API

This endpoint allows you to send a message to a user on Instagram.

## Request

### Request Body

- `recipient.id` (string, required): The Instagram user ID of the recipient.

- `message.text` (string, required): The text of the message to be sent.


Example:

``` json
{
  "recipient": {
    "id": "{{instagram_scoped_id}}"
  },
  "message": {
    "text": "Hello World!"
  }
}

 ```

## Response

Example response

``` json
{
  "recipient_id": "IGSID",
  "message_id": "MESSAGE-ID"
}

 ```

- `message_id` (string): The ID of the sent message.

